2011年9月，[[三星電子|三星]]和英特爾與Linux基金會宣布致力在2012年開發出Tizen，希望用來取代[[MeeGo|MeeGo]]專案。<ref>{{cite web |last=Toor |first=Amar |url=http://www.engadget.com/2011/09/28/meego-to-be-folded-into-linux-based-tizen- os-slated-to-arrive-i/ |title=MeeGo to be folded into Linux-based Tizen OS, slated to arrive in 2012 |publisher=Engadget |date=2011-09-28 |accessdate=2011-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303201142/http://www.engadget.com/2011/09/28/meego-to-be-folded-into-linux-based-tizen-/ |archive-date=2017-03-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ricker |first=Thomas |url=http://thisismynext.com/2011/09/28/meego-dead-meet-tizen-open-source-os-based -linux/ |title=MeeGo is dead: Resurrected as Tizen, the newest Linux-based open source OS |publisher=The Verge |date=2011-09-28 |accessdate=2011-12-18 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=OTk1Mg |title=Tizen Is Announced; MeeGo Will Transition To It |date=2011-10-19 |author=Michael Larabel |work=phoronix.com |accessdate=2011-12-20 |archive-date=2012-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120101001815/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=OTk1Mg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="welcome" /><ref name="rebooted"/>參與開發的廠商有[[英特爾|英特爾]]、[[三星電子|三星]]、[[富士通|富士通]]、[[華為|華為]]、[[NEC|NEC]]、[[KT公司|KT公司]]（韓國通訊）、[[NTT_DoCoMo|NTT DoCoMo]]、[[法國電信|Orange]]、[[Panasonic|Panasonic]]、[[SK集团|SK]]、[[Sprint|Sprint]]、[[Vodafone|Vodafone]]等。<ref name="welcome">{{cite web|last=Foster|first=Dawn|title=Welcome to Tizen!|url=https://www.tizen.org/blogs/dawnfoster/2011/welcome-tizen|publisher=tizen.org|accessdate=2011-09-28|archive-date=2011-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013071516/https://www.tizen.org/blogs/dawnfoster/2011/welcome-tizen|dead-url=no}}</ref>之前曾經支持MeeGo專案的[[諾基亞|諾基亞]]則將獨立發展另一個後繼專案[[Meltemi|Meltemi]]，目標將專注於[[功能手機|功能手機]]。MeeGo仍然有效，<ref name="rebooted">{{cite web|last=Paul|first=Ryan|title=MeeGo rebooted as Intel and Samsung launch new Tizen platform|url=http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2011/09/meego-rebooted-as-intel-and-samsung-launch-new-tizen-platform.ars|publisher=Ars Technica|accessdate=2011-09-28|archive-date=2011-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110929201632/http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2011/09/meego-rebooted-as-intel-and-samsung-launch-new-tizen-platform.ars|dead-url=no}}</ref>社群以此開發了另一個專案[[Mer|Mer]]。

2012年1月1日，LiMo基金會更名為Tizen協會。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://embedded-m2m-solutions.tmcnet.com/topics/sprint-news/articles/289278-sprint-joins-tizen-association-adds-its-board-directors.htm|title=Sprint News - Sprint Joins Tizen Association, Adds to its Board of Directors|date=2012-05-07|author=Rory Lidstone|publisher=embedded-m2m-solutions|accessdate=2014-10-09|language=en|archive-date=2014-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014184852/http://embedded-m2m-solutions.tmcnet.com/topics/sprint-news/articles/289278-sprint-joins-tizen-association-adds-its-board-directors.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>以推動Tizen，包括需求整合，產品識別和促進服務模式，以及整體行業營銷和教育。Tizen的開發者希望能夠強化[[HTML5|HTML5]]的應用。

2012年1月17日，三星宣布將[[Bada_(操作系统)|Bada]]整合至Tizen。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.cnyes.com/Content/20120117/KFHZDGPY1FGXU.shtml?c=pic|title=三星加快擺脫Android拉攏英特爾合作OS|publisher=[[鉅亨網|鉅亨網]]|date=2012-01-17|language=zh-tw|access-date=2012-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130309001704/http://news.cnyes.com/Content/20120117/KFHZDGPY1FGXU.shtml?c=pic|archive-date=2013-03-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>4月30日，Tizen釋出1.0版，開發代號為彩雀（Larkspur）。同年9月25日，Tizen釋出2.0 alpha版，開發代號為玉蘭（Magnolia）。

