th-phones-and-tv-to-follow-nokia-signs-on-for-maps/ | archivedate=2014-01-22 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年底，[[Sprint|Sprint]]和[[Telefónica|Telefónica]]離開Tizen協會。Telefónica將重心轉移至[[Firefox_OS|Firefox OS]]。[[NTT_DoCoMo|NTT DoCoMo]]宣稱依然重視Tizen。法國營運商[[法國電信|Orange]]稱Tizen開發速度不如預期。不過NTT DoCoMo與Orange依然是Tizen Association的成員。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/t/2014-02-03/10019140615.shtml|title=三星新操作系统遇挫：多家运营商停止支持|publisher=[[新浪科技|新浪科技]]|date=2014-02-03|language=zh-cn|accessdate=2014-02-13|archive-date=2014-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213225509/http://tech.sina.com.cn/t/2014-02-03/10019140615.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fiercewireless.com/story/report-sprint-docomo-and-other-carriers-back-away-samsungs-tizen/2014-02-03|title=Sprint, DoCoMo and other carriers back away from Samsung's Tizen|publisher=[[FierceWireless|FierceWireless]]|date=2014-02-04|language=en-us|accessdate=2014-02-27|archive-date=2014-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305153644/http://www.fiercewireless.com/story/report-sprint-docomo-and-other-carriers-back-away-samsungs-tizen/2014-02-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

